feedbackPlaceholder.message:
Please copy the plug-in data from another computer (remember to click the Copy button for initializing data) and paste it here. The replacement plug-in data is usually used for initializing plug-in data. 
 Only the plug-in data can be stored locally due to the limitation of the data synchronization capacity of the Google plug-in Manifest v3 version. Therefore, this method is used to initialize data.
